      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and balanced weight distribution this chassis is known for. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved performance vehicle, the mechanical vitals are strong, delivering a linear power band and a 8,000 RPM redline that defines the analog M-car era.",
